# Design System Rules

## Components

- IMPORTANT: Use components from `components/ui/` for all UI elements
- Never recreate a Button, Input, Modal, or other primitive ŌĆö use the design system component
- `components/blocks/` sections must only compose `components/ui/` primitives
- New UI components go in `components/ui/`
- New page sections go in `components/blocks/`

## Tokens

- All tokens are CSS custom properties defined in `src/styles/tokens.css`
- IMPORTANT: Never use hardcoded colors (`#000`, `rgb(...)`, Tailwind palette colors like `bg-zinc-900`)
- Use semantic token classes via Tailwind: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `text-foreground-subtle`, `bg-muted-background`, `text-muted-foreground`, `ring-ring`
- For button states use the dedicated button token variables: `var(--buttons-button-primary-background)`, etc.
- Typography: use semantic scale classes only ŌĆö `display-large`, `headline-large`, `title-medium`, `body-large`, `label-medium`, etc. (never raw `text-3xl` or similar)
- Spacing: use Tailwind spacing scale only (`p-8`, `gap-4`, `py-24`)

## Layout

- All sections: `<section className="py-24"><div className="max-w-[--content] mx-auto px-6">...</div></section>`
- Default section spacing: `py-24` ┬Ę Dense: `py-16`
- Default gap: `gap-8` ┬Ę Large sections: `gap-12` or `gap-16`

## Styling Constraints

- Tailwind utility classes only ŌĆö no inline styles, no CSS Modules
- IMPORTANT: No arbitrary Tailwind values (`px-[18px]`, `text-[#333]`)
- Border radius: `rounded-lg` or `rounded-3xl` only
- Borders: `border` or `border-2` only
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/utils.ts` for all class merging
- All components must accept a `className` prop

## Code Conventions

- TypeScript, functional components, named exports
- React 19: pass `ref` as a prop directly (not via `React.forwardRef`)
- Use `@base-ui/react` primitives for accessible interactive components
- Use `cva()` only for multi-variant components (Button, Badge, Alert)

## Files to Reference

- `src/styles/tokens.css` ŌĆö all CSS custom property tokens (auto-generated, do not edit)
- `src/lib/utils.ts` ŌĆö `cn()` helper
- `components/ui/Button.tsx` ŌĆö canonical multi-variant component pattern
- `tokens/*.json` ŌĆö Figma token source files
- `scripts/generate-tokens-css.mjs` ŌĆö token build script (`pnpm tokens:build`)
